metadata.name: Mandala of Love
metadata.description:
Mandala of love. 
One of the most powerful mandalas to help you find love. - Draw love...
- And how to do it? 
- Draw what you feel... 
- I feel a frenzy of colors, a thrill in my body! Subtle vibrations of my soul. The desire to give all of yourself! 
- You're right! Draw!!!
